  "texts": [
    "Root cause analysisThe root cause analysis feature allows users to determine the type of errors or threats their system faces by reading parameter sensor values in the customized factory CSV file.",
    "Table 4 from our previous work [8] displays the different types of sensors used for the \"root cause analysis\" use case.",
    "We test our two industrial bots' versions with the following root cause analysis prompts: Synthetic data generationThe synthetic data generation feature is used to create various data using the model in the customized factory CSV data as Fig. 9 Faulty equipment discovery prompt result from the online bot version a template.",
    "This feature is useful when needing more data to train machine learning models or when performing analytical tasks and activities requiring additional data.",
    "Our work in [8] provides more guidelines on using this task with our customized industrial chatbot."
  ]
}